		<img class="icons_group2" src="/resource/Lightning_designing_style/assets/icons/utility/clock_60.png"></img>
		<span class="date-adress"> 24th December 2016 from 14:00 to 18:00</span>
		<br></br>
		<img class="icons_group2" src="/resource/Lightning_designing_style/assets/icons/utility/checkin_60.png"></img>
		<span class="date-adress"> Senate House Malet Street, London</span>
		<img class="icons_group1" src="/resource/CORE_LA_StaticResource/event_app/images/Saved.png"></img>
	</div>
	<div  onclick="{!c.gotoDetail}" class="events-cards">Creative Writing
		<span class="lang">(English)</span>
		<br></br>
		<span class="num-attendees">30 Attending</span>
        <img class="facility" src="/resource/CORE_LA_StaticResource/event_app/images/facility.png"></img>
        <hr></hr>
		<img class="event-banner" src="/resource/CORE_LA_StaticResource/event_app/images/event_image_dummy3.png"></img>
		<br></br>This event covers elements of three major creative writing genres: short story, narrative essay, and memoir. You will master the techniques that good writers use to compose a bracing story, populated with memorable characters in an interesting setting, written in a fresh descriptive style. You will analyze and constructively evaluate peer writing. In the Capstone, you will draft, rewrite, and complete a substantial original story in the genre of your choosing.
        
		<hr></hr>
		<img class="icons_group2" src="/resource/Lightning_designing_style/assets/icons/utility/clock_60.png"></img>
		<span class="date-adress"> 24th December 2016 from 14:00 to 18:00</span>
		<br></br>
		<img class="icons_group2" src="/resource/Lightning_designing_style/assets/icons/utility/checkin_60.png"></img>
		<span class="date-adress"> Senate House Malet Street, London</span>
		<img class="icons_group1" src="/resource/Lightning_designing_style/assets/icons/utility/check_60.png"></img>
	</div>
	<button class="slds-button slds-button--neutral show-more"> View more</button>
    

</aura:component>